I looked into the situation with a fully open mind just looking for truth...and I do think the ppl Iran first of all are well aware that declaring war against the US and pushing for revenge as they are, means they are either too propaganda driven to grasp the suicidal implications of this war which would be the first real major power conflict since ww2 with the potential for such massive political and mortal fallout for both sides but it’s easy to see if Russia stays out of it and regardless of Israel’s move (the party who’s been praying for us to take out khomeni since bush and Obama nailed the rest of their hit list), Iran is fucked beyond belief. I hope we use restraint on the American side but location and natural/middle defenses as well as the ability to move soldiers quickly as well as bomb from any point on the globe In shocking rapid time, makes a landlocked developed nation like Iran one of the weakest opponents for the us just based on Logistics and geographical context.

I can’t help but wonder if trumps goal was to satisfy the Israeli/neocon American target list, which I also suspected with that false flag nonsense in Syria w chemical weapons that served the state no benefit but to add another major power to their enemies...so I suspect any democrat or republican of serving our strange interests this way but regardless of the fact of a moral lapse or just cause, I can’t imagine how Iran without all allies against a solo us could stand a chance regardless that they would be the best military we’ve faced in a very long time. Iran also has Israel sitting right across the street with the best defense systems ever created and a mysterious but likely very impressive array of weapons of mass destruction including nuclear weaponry for decades now. If Russia can stay on the high ground and keep to their own business they should be rewarded with a much improved business partner in the uS and suffer only the loss of an upstart mediocre ally. In the post soviet era I can’t grasper Why we haven’t become far closer with the Russians. As close allies with a treaty against conflict between each other we could remain the top two powers on earth for as far as one can predict on current trends in global politics.

If we ship out fully to Iran, this better Be our last middle eastern dance for a millennia
